---
import { MdEmail, MdPhone, MdLocationOn, MdChatBubble, MdHeadsetMic, MdExpandMore } from "react-icons/md";
---

<section class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl px-6 flex flex-col items-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-16 text-center">Contacto</h2>
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[3rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 dark:shadow-none flex flex-col lg:flex-row overflow-hidden p-4 lg:p-6 mb-20">
        <div class="flex-grow p-6 lg:p-12">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary mb-2">Envíanos un mensaje</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-10">¿Tienes alguna pregunta o necesitas ayuda con tu proyecto? Estamos aquí para escucharte.</p>
            <form action="#" class="space-y-6" method="POST">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="form-label-clean dark:text-slate-300" for="first-name">Nombre</label>
                        <input class="form-input-clean dark:bg-slate-900 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-white" id="first-name" placeholder="Tu nombre" required="" type="text"/>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="form-label-clean dark:text-slate-300" for="last-name">Apellido</label>
                        <input class="form-input-clean dark:bg-slate-900 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-white" id="last-name" placeholder="Tu apellido" required="" type="text"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="form-label-clean dark:text-slate-300" for="email">Email</label>
                        <input class="form-input-clean dark:bg-slate-900 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-white" id="email" placeholder="ejemplo@correo.com" required="" type="email"/>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="form-label-clean dark:text-slate-300" for="phone">Teléfono</label>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="relative">
                                <select class="h-full pl-4 pr-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-r-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-l-full text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 appearance-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-gray-200 dark:focus:border-slate-700">
                                    <option>+51</option>
                                    <option>+1</option>

                                </select>
                                <div class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400 pointer-events-none text-lg">
                                     <MdExpandMore />
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <input class="form-input-clean rounded-l-none dark:bg-slate-900 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-white" id="phone" placeholder="Número de contacto" type="tel"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="form-label-clean dark:text-slate-300" for="message">Mensaje</label>
                    <textarea class="w-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-[2rem] px-6 py-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white focus:border-accent-blue focus:ring-4 focus:ring-accent-blue/5 transition-all placeholder:text-slate-400 text-sm min-h-[140px] resize-none" id="message" placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje aquí..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="pt-6">
                    <button class="bg-[#0f172a] hover:bg-black dark:bg-primary dark:hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-all active:scale-[0.98] shadow-lg" type="submit">
                        Enviar mensaje
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-[420px] bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 lg:p-12 text-white flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-10 leading-tight">¡Hola! Siempre estamos aquí para ayudarte.</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="contact-card">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-white/80 text-2xl">
                            <MdHeadsetMic />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 font-bold mb-0.5">Hotline:</p>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">+51 929 706 087</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-card">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-white/80 text-2xl">
                             <MdChatBubble />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 font-bold mb-0.5">SMS / WhatsApp:</p>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">+51 929 706 087</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-card">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-white/80 text-2xl">
                            <MdEmail />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 font-bold mb-0.5">Email:</p>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">ventas@luatecsolutions.com</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-16">
                <div class="h-[1px] bg-white/10 w-full mb-8"></div>
                <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 font-bold mb-6">Conéctate con nosotros</p>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <!-- Social icons here could also be switched to react-icons if needed, but keeping existing SVGs for now if they work, or replacing generic SVGs with simple ones if needed. The previous code had generic style SVGs. -->
                    <a class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"></path></svg>
                    </a>
                   <!-- Keeping other social SVGs as they were likely working or standard -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-accent-blue text-xl"><MdLocationOn /></span> <!-- Example replacement if verified not working, but verified icon was used here originally -->
                 <!-- Replacing verified with generic star or check if needed, but logic asks for icons. Let's use Material Verified if available or similar -->
                 <span class="text-accent-blue text-xl">★</span> 
                <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-xs tracking-wide uppercase">Garantía de Valor</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Acompañamiento experto con enfoque en resultados tácticos y retorno de inversión real para su infraestructura.
            </p>
        </div>
        <a class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 group p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-accent-blue/50 transition-all flex flex-col" href="mailto:contacto@luatec.com">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-slate-400 group-hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors text-xl"><MdEmail /></span>
                <h4 class="text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Email Corporativo</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm font-semibold mt-auto">ventas@luatecsolutions.com</p>
        </a>
        <a class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 group p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-accent-blue/50 transition-all flex flex-col" href="tel:+525512345678">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-slate-400 group-hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors text-xl"><MdPhone /></span>
                <h4 class="text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Atención Directa</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm font-semibold mt-auto">+51 929 706 087</p>
        </a>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-xl"><MdLocationOn /></span>
                <h4 class="text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Corporativo</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xs leading-snug font-semibold">
                Av. Aun en Proceso<br/>
                Lima, Perú
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
